Introduction

ASC2NT is a five-member boy group under New Ways Company. They made their debut on May 7, 2024, with the single album "Expecting Tomorrow".

On December 21, 2023, New Ways Company revealed that three former DGNA members who appeared on Peak Time—Karam, Injun, and Jay—had signed exclusive contracts with them and would re-debut in a new group.

The company introduced two additional members, Reon and Kyle, via SNS accounts on January 16, 2024. Finally, on April 15, 2024, ASC2NT officially announced their debut date and the release of their first single album. Notably, all ASC2NT members have completed their military service prior to debut.

On July 17 2024 they took to social media to announce the fandom name "Eppy" short for Episode. Meaning the members and fans will create "Episodes" together.
